<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>إِلَّا فِي جُمُعَةٍ وَعِيدٍ تَعَذَّرَا خَلْفَ غَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَتَصِحُّ خَلْفَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- أَعْمَى أَصَمَّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَأَقْلَفَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَأَقْطَعَ يَدَيْنِ، أَوْ رِجْلَيْنِ، أَوْ أَنْفٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَكَثِيرِ لَحْنٍ لَمْ يُحِلِ المَعْنَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> لَا خَلْفَ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- أَخْرَسَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَكَافِرٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَلَا إِمَامَةُ عَاجِزٍ عَنْ شَرْطٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> أَوْ رُكْنٍ:</span> إِلَّا بِمِثْلِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> إِلَّا الإِمَامَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> الرَّاتِبَ بِمَسْجِدٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> المَرْجُوَّ زَوَالُ عِلَّتِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- فَيُصَلِّي جَالِسًا، وَيَجْلِسُونَ خَلْفَهُ، وَتَصِحُّ قِيَامًا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَلَا إِمَامَةُ امْرَأَةٍ وَخُنْثَى لِرِجَالٍ أَوْ خَنَاثَى.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>- وَلَا مُمَيِّزٍ لِبَالِغٍ فِي فَرْضٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>